&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" src='https://actforjason.github.io/posts/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9daz-studio-ui%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F/images/1757507143419.png' alt="enter description here" height="512" width="640"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>压缩所有提交</title><link>https://actforjason.github.io/posts/%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4/</link><pubDate>Fri, 05 Sep 2025 17:18:30 +0800</pubDate><author>actforzjz@gmail.com (Jason)</author><guid>https://actforjason.github.io/posts/%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4/</guid><category domain="https://actforjason.github.io/categories/%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6/">版本控制</category><category domain="https://actforjason.github.io/categories/intellij-idea/">Intellij IDEA</category><description>&lt;p&gt;想把 &lt;strong&gt;当前分支的所有提交&lt;/strong&gt; 压缩成一个提交，但是分支里有一些 &lt;strong&gt;Merge Commit（本地和远程的合并提交）&lt;/strong&gt;,也就是说，历史不是线性的，不能直接用普通 &lt;code&gt;git rebase -i&lt;/code&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Markdown Syntax Guide</title><link>https://actforjason.github.io/posts/markdown-syntax/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>actforzjz@gmail.com (Jason)</author><guid>https://actforjason.github.io/posts/markdown-syntax/</guid><category domain="https://actforjason.github.io/categories/markdown/">Markdown</category><description>&lt;p&gt;This article offers a sample of basic Markdown syntax that can be used in Hugo content files, also it shows whether basic HTML elements are decorated with CSS in a Hugo theme.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>